(India has long baffled theorists of democracy. Democratic theory holds t\hat poverty, )Tj
0 -1.2 TD
(widespread illiteracy, and a deeply hierarchical social structure are in\hospitable conditions )Tj
0 -1.561 TD
(for the functioning of democracy. )Tj
